dct_title_s: Map of Shrewsbury River from Gunning Island to Turnpike Bridge at Seabright compiled from surveys of 1897 and 1891
dct_description_sm: Map of Shrewsbury River from Gunning Island to Turnpike Bridge at Seabright compiled from surveys of 1887 and 1891. Soundings are expressed in feet and refer to mean low water.
